                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 text-center">
                    <h5>
                        <strong>MyNote</strong>
                    </h5>
                    <p>Copyright &copy; myNote @DateTime.Now.Year</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 text-center">
                    <h5>
                        <strong>E-bülten</strong>
                    </h5>


                    <div class="col-md-12">
                        <p>Sapien elit in malesuada semper mi, id sollicitudin urna fermentum.</p>
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <input type="text" placeholder="email adresiniz" class="form-control" />
                            <span class="input-group-btn">
                                <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">
                                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-send"></span> Kaydet
